products.title: Casual Shirt
products.description: This shirt is made from 100% cotton, making it soft to the touch and gentle on the skin. The long-sleeve design is perfect for those cooler days or nights, while the button-up closure makes it easy to take on and off. The plaid design is perfect for any casual occasion, whether going to a barbecue or running errands. The shirt is made in Italy, so you know you’re getting a high-quality product.

products.title: Sky Grey Rib-Knit Full Sleeves Shirt
products.description: Elevate your everyday wardrobe with our sky grey rib-knit full sleeves shirts for men, featuring a spread collar and relaxed fit. Made with cotton fabric, the rib knit shirt offers the perfect combination of warmth, comfort, and style. Dress it up or down with jeans or trousers.

products.title: Green Regular Fit Full Sleeves Shirt
products.description: A lush green piece of art that adds a refreshing tone, giving your presence a refined edge; perfect for both casual hangouts and dressed-up moments. Crafted from breathable fabric, this Green Regular Fit Full Sleeves Shirt moves with you effortlessly. Button it up for a polished look, or wear it open over a tee for laid-back charm—either way, you own the room.

products.title: Grey Stripe Shirt
products.description: Bold verticals, but make it breezy. This grey printed stripe shirt isn’t just about symmetry—it’s about making statements. The classic collar and clean silhouette give it polish, while the punchy stripes add a laid-back edge. Pair it with denim or tapered trousers; this one’s made for moods that swing between serious and spontaneous.
